  "@type": "Domain",
  "critical": false,
  "description": "Domestication, husbandry, and utilization of animals for food, fiber, motive power, transport, and materials. Animals provide critical inputs across the tech tree: draft power (the primary motive force before steam), leather (durable flexible material), wool (insulating fiber), tallow (first lubricant and candle fuel), bone and horn (tool materials), sinew (high-tensile cordage), and dairy products.",
